      "raw": "The Dirac operator acts on L^2(SU(3), S) = bigoplus_{(p,q)} V_{(p,q)} x V_{(p,q)}^* x S.",
      "type": "code",
      "context": "By the Peter-Weyl theorem, L^2(SU(3)) = bigoplus_{(p,q)} V_{(p,q)} x V_{(p,q)}^*.",
      "session": "",
      "source_file": "tier0-computation\\tier1_spectral_action.py",
