      "new_latex": "",
      "new_status": "",
      "error_note": "",
      "severity": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "eq_11716",
      "raw": "So the weight is dim(p,q) (= dim(p,q)^2 / dim(p,q), since D_{(p,q)} already",
      "type": "code",
      "context": "Tr(f(D^2/L^2)) includes dim(p,q) copies of each D_{(p,q)} eigenvalue.",
